Mission

CoreBioPathways aims to provide scientific guidance and data analysis to clients with an emphasis on experimental vigor and actionable insights based on client needs.

Services we offer

  • Bioinformatics analysis of projects; genomics, transcriptomics, proteomics
  • Bioanalytical assay analysis
  • Data Analysis and Dissemination: Dashboard and App development, Machine learning Projects
  • Subject matter expertise:microbiology, microbiomes, immunology, oncology, cell therapies, biological networks
  • Laboratory operations: Equipment and consumable strategizing.

Data Analytics

  • Data analytics for biological studies
  • R, python, Bash workflows
  • Dashboards (dash, quarto) and application development (shiny)
  • Data management and pipelines

Bioinformatics

CoreBioPathways experts have experience with several bioinformatics analyses and workflows; including:

  • Genomics (whole exome and whole genome sequencing)
  • Transcriptomics (bulk and single cell RNAseq)
  • Proteomics

Laboratory Consulting

  • Assessment of laboratory operations for cost reductions and efficiency improvements
  • Laboratory operations, equipment, and consumable strategizing.
  • Implementation of best practices in laboratory management
  • Training and support for laboratory personnel in molecular biology techniques and data/programming

Subject Matter Expertise

  • In-depth knowledge in: Microbiology, Immunology, Microbiomes, Cell Therapies, Oncology, Bioinformatics, Automation development in R and Python
  • Consultation on research projects, grant applications, and publications
  • Literature reviews and white paper level strategy analysis
